Creational Pattern

The implementation of singleton pattern has always been a controversial topic among developers.

Pattern
http://www.gofpatterns.com/design-patterns/module2/three-types-design-patterns.php

Singleton, pattern or antipattern
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12755539/why-is-singleton-considered-an-anti-pattern
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11292109/why-implementing-a-singleton-pattern-in-java-code-is-sometimes-considered-an-a


Commons concepts to implement singleton pattern

* private construct to avoid instantiationof the class from other class
* private static variable of the same class
* public and static method  that returns the instance of the class


